<DIV2 N="3" TYPE="chapter">
<PB N="222" REF="121">
<HEAD>CHAP. III. Multiplication.</HEAD>
<P>_MVltiplication is the as|sumption of one num|ber, as many times as the other, containeth in it selfe vnities.
