<DIV2 N="5" TYPE="chapter">
<PB N="228" REF="124">
<HEAD>CHAP. V. Rules of Fractions.</HEAD>
<P>_A Fraction is a number no|ting the <HI>partes aliquot</HI> of an entire or whole num|ber, whereof it is said to be a fraction as a penny, the twelfth part of a shilling, one inch the foure and fortieth part of an Ell, &amp;c.</P>
</DIV2>
<DIV2 N="6" TYPE="chapter">
